<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 1.75; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">5月27日下午，我校在行政楼一楼会议室召开意识形态、平安建设工作专题会议。会议由党委书记、督导专员江延湖主持，党委副书记、执行校长范红铭，党委副书记高建国，副校长徐国荣、梅龙、傅志军、朱军、吴志勇以及党政办、组织部、宣传部、统战部、教师工作部、学工处、保卫处、团委、教务处、信息中心主要负责人、各党总支书记出席会议。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 1.75; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 1.75; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-06-01%2021%3A31%3A23%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%871.png?Expires=2032608683&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=mdeKGyv8tsL2r5e5hV48u258AEw%3D" alt="" width="650" height="424" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 1.75; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 1.75; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">会议传达了上级相关文件和会议精神，高建国副书记就近期学校安全稳定工作进行了部署；宣传部、保卫处、信息中心、信访办分别通报了近期学校意识形态领域和舆情风险、安全情况、2024年一季度学校网络安全、信访工作，并进行了分析研判。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 1.75; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">范红铭校长指出，意识形态和校园安全稳定是学校各项事业能够顺利发展的前提，各部门、各学院要高度重视这两项工作，对影响意识形态、安全稳定的问题做到心中有数、手中有策，超前部署、超前掌控，提前做好防范和处置措施。要切实提高执行力，提高主动性，行动起来，确保取得实效；要坚持担当作为，打起万分精神，提升战斗力，确保各项工作高质量完成。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 1.75; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">江延湖书记强调，<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">一是</strong>要认清形势，深入研判，提高警觉，扎实落实。要把党纪学习教育，与改进工作作风、师德师风及学风教风同步推进；<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">二是</strong>要强化制度建设<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">，</strong>强化管理，注重质量，提升水平，形成常态化机制；<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">三要</strong>加强阵地管理，全覆盖、无死角守好课堂阵地、实践阵地、网络阵地，持续开展专项清查；<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">四要</strong>加强风险研判，提高舆情处置能力，不断提升舆情敏感性，加强舆情应对能力；<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">五要</strong>畅通师生诉求通道，积极响应学生诉求，把“时时放心不下”的责任感转化为“事事心中有底”的行动力。</span></p><p><br/></p>